12 SECTION 7. INTERNATIONAL PEACE GARDEN. The International Peace Garden line
13 item in section 1 of this Act includes $1,717,500 for projects at the International Peace Garden,
14 which the parks and recreation department may provide only to the extent the funds are
15 matched by the province of Manitoba at a value equal to the United States dollar exchange rate
16 on July 1, 2025.
17 SECTION 8. A new section to chapter 55-08 of the North Dakota Century Code is created
18 and enacted as follows:
19 Creation and naming of state parks.
20 Notwithstanding any other provision of law, a state agency or official may not create a new
21 state park or rename an existing state park without prior approval from the legislative assembly.
